Subject: Re: [T2] Electric fuel pump with stock dual carbs???

On Fri, 2 Dec 2005, John Baker wrote:

> ...What I want to know is:  Will the aftermarket
> universal electric fuel pump (it is rated to give 3-4
> psi of pressure) work with the stock dual carbs?? If
> so, is it as easy as putting a "T" in the fuel line to
> supply both sides??


Yes to both.  As long as the flow rate is enough to satisfy those hungry
carbs, it will work fine.

Be sure to be workmanlike in the running of the lines.  Don't leave long
runs hanging in space!

George
